{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2334646, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谁来补偿？🤷🏼‍♀️", "timestamp": 1629629956, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334649, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": 2334646, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你情我愿为什么要强制补偿", "timestamp": 1629630011, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334661, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可以，自己的选择。一个孩子可能以后也是一年几十万", "timestamp": 1629630144, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334662, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": 2334649, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: “生孩子多痛苦，不给补偿你自己去生啊”", "timestamp": 1629630152, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334671, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有些是传统必要的东西非要用钱的话", "timestamp": 1629630254, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334685, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就像房子就算租一辈子也不用一千万啊", "timestamp": 1629630382, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334693, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "也许如果想赚钱，最优解也不是现在在清华浪费时间吧", "timestamp": 1629630504, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334727, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不对，原假设忽略了女生在孕期暂时离开工作岗位导致失去的潜在升职加薪机会，如果因为生孩子导致晋升晚了两年（这种事情很多时候都不一定能平移，错过了就错过了），那么假设之后每年她的薪水都比不生孩子的情况下低20%，以为祖国健康工作五十年算，这成本起码500w+起步", "timestamp": 1629630714, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334778, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": 2334685, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 跟房子还不一样吧，房子还有学区属性，还可以变卖，这，又不能", "timestamp": 1629631192, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334815, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在中国一年几十万不买房不生娃留着干什么，都用来消费吗。没有孩子就没有家族，剩下的财产捐赠社会吗", "timestamp": 1629631445, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334825, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果想好抛弃传统不婚或者不育应该规划一下以后怎么办", "timestamp": 1629631556, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334836, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": 2334825, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 普通家庭多少是因为有孩子才带来了许多生机", "timestamp": 1629631648, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334873, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": 2334671, "tag": null, "text": "洞友们会认为如果自己的父母没有孩子，现在会生活地更美满更幸福吗。\n有些东西可能都不需要回报，只要拿在手里就很满足。就像那句“你甚至都不愿意叫我一声教父”一样的情感", "timestamp": 1629631921, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334908, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": 2334873, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 额，没必要吵吧，个人选择，你有结婚的权利，别人也有不婚的权利，没必要硬说别人过的不好吧", "timestamp": 1629632191, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334918, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": 2334908, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 只是合理的劝说", "timestamp": 1629632270, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334928, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": 2334908, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我觉得还是要感谢这个社会，以前的人们都被迫结婚，现在大家有了选择的权利，觉得自己成本太高可以选择不结，这种自由还是可贵的", "timestamp": 1629632372, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334944, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "敢尝试的就尝试吧我只是感觉以后肯定后悔", "timestamp": 1629632494, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2334958, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "自由是过程不是结果", "timestamp": 1629632627, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2335031, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你开始算这个成本就是把这个事情当成生意……那无论多少钱也不应该生，建议不要谈恋爱 因为谈恋爱大概率也是负收益", "timestamp": 1629633274, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2335090, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": 2335031, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 看情况讨论吧，婚姻应该是两个人共赢，但有些一方吸血另一方的婚姻真的没必要", "timestamp": 1629633868, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2335122, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 446982, "reply_to": 2335090, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 可能更重要的是和谁生而不是生不生", "timestamp": 1629634110, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 1, "pid": 446982, "reply": 21, "tag": null, "text": "服气，清华女生生育成本65-85万洞，如果洞友觉得不对，请拿出自己的计算方案，列在本洞\n不要做“你不对”，“虽然我不会但是我反对”的事情\n欢迎来稿", "timestamp": 1629629833, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629634110, "url": "", "vote": {}}}